-- Conergy Sued by Investors Over Disappointing Results, FTD Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2011-12-21T08:08:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-21/conergy-sued-by-investors-over-disappointing-results-ftd-says.html
Conergy AG faces a legal test case
at a Hamburg court in March, after 17 shareholders sued the
company for 3.5 million euros ($4.6 million) because they were
disappointed about its financial situation in 2007, the
 Financial Times Deutschland  reported today, without saying where
it obtained the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
